WEBVTT

00:02:26.241 --> 00:02:30.066
And apparently,
an octopus can also open a jar.

00:02:31.883 --> 00:02:33.637
It's pretty impressive, right?

00:02:35.918 --> 00:02:40.418
But clearly, this is not enabled
just by the brain of this animal,

00:02:40.442 --> 00:02:42.456
but also by his body,

00:02:42.480 --> 00:02:46.512
and it's a clear example,
maybe the clearest example,

00:02:46.536 --> 00:02:48.336
of embodied intelligence,

00:02:48.360 --> 00:02:51.646
which is a kind of intelligence
that all living organisms have.

00:02:51.670 --> 00:02:53.236
We all have that.

00:02:53.260 --> 00:02:57.102
Our body, its shape,
material and structure,

00:02:57.126 --> 00:03:00.308
plays a fundamental role
during a physical task,